                            <strong>The Lesson:</strong><br>
                            Just like the RAF only looked at returning planes, we often in business life only look at survivors.<br>
                            For example, we think "Being First" is a necessary key to success, because we ignore the many pioneers that failed.<br><br>
                            <span style="font-size:12px; color:#000000; font-weight: 600;">(Reference: Golder & Tellis, 1993 - "Pioneer Advantage: Marketing Logic or Marketing Legend?")</span>
